TITLE: Override root element props directly - React
DESCRIPTION: This shows a simplified way to override the root element's properties by directly passing them into 'componentProps'. This is a shorthand for setting the 'root' prop.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gijs-epping/plasmic-docs/blob/main/learn/react-api/.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
&lt;PlasmicComponent
component=&quot;Button&quot;
// This is interpreted as a prop override for the `root` element
componentProps={{onClick:()=&gt;alert(&#x27;I got clicked!&#x27;)}}
/&gt;
```

