TITLE: Override root element with onClick handler - React
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to override the 'root' element of a Plasmic 'Button' component and attach an onClick event handler using the 'componentProps' prop.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gijs-epping/plasmic-docs/blob/main/learn/react-api/.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
&lt;PlasmicComponent
component=&quot;Button&quot;
componentProps={{
root:{
props:{
onClick:()=&gt;alert(&#x27;I got clicked!&#x27;)
}
}
}}
/&gt;
```

