TITLE: Update Plasmic CMS Item JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to update an existing item in Plasmic CMS using the API. It requires the CMS ID, secret token, and the row ID of the item to update. The code constructs a JSON object representing the updates to be applied and sends a PUT request to the Plasmic API endpoint.
