TITLE: Catch-All Component Implementation
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet creates the catch-all component that loads and renders Plasmic pages based on the current route. It uses the `PLASMIC` loader to fetch component data and the `<plasmic-component>` directive to render the Plasmic content.  It also handles loading and error states.
