TITLE: useSafeParams Hook with useSelector
DESCRIPTION: This code defines a custom hook `useSafeParams` that attempts to retrieve router parameters. It first tries to get parameters from the `useRouter` hook. If that fails (e.g., during pre-rendering), it falls back to using `useSelector` to access parameters stored in the data context under the key 'params'. This allows components to access parameters even when the router is not fully initialized.
